Locusts Plague 1.5 Million Hectares in Russia, Government Says

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-06-21T15:39:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/locusts-plague-1-5-million-hectares-in-russia-government-says.html
Locusts landed on at least 1.5
million hectares (3.7 million acres) of crops in the Russian
Federation, the  Agriculture Ministry  said.  Some 5.7 million hectares of crops were inspected, the
ministry said today in an e-mailed statement, without
elaborating on the regions, types of crops affected or the
extent of damage caused.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  